title: Statin
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set intends to capture generic and brand codes for Statins),(Data Element Scope: Intentionally left blank),(Inclusion Criteria: All generics (with different strengths) and brands (with different strengths) for single ingredient statins and combination statins; includes ingridients (IN), precise ingredient (PIN), clinical drug component (SCDC),  clinical drug/ pack (SCD/GPCK), clinical dose form group (SCDG), dose form group (DFG), brand names (BN), branded drug component (SBDC), brand drug pack (SBD/BPCK) and branded dose from group (SBDG)),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes PCSK9i, Ezetimibe, Bile Acid Sequestrants, Fibrates, Niacin and Omega-3 fatty acids)
